Package: MetaScope
Type: Package
Title: This package contains tools and functions for preprocessing microbiome data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: W. Evan Johnson
Maintainer: W. Evan Johnson <wej@bu.edu>
Description: This package contains the tools and methods for preprocessing microbiome data
    It contains tools for library generation, demultiplexing, alignment, microbe identification
    Is is essentially an R translation of PathoScope 2.0, or MetaScope
